title: CoD4 MultiHack PB-Undetected April 2014 (Newest SOH)
description:
Hi, 




This is The Newest SOH MultiHack for Call of Duty 4. 

It is PB-Undetected, so you can safely join any punkbuster server. 

I tested this myself.


Instructions:

-Unpack the .rar file with winrar or 7zip. 

-Start the SoH 5.5 CoD4.exe. (You will hear a sound when it starts.)

-You will see some kind of C4 Bomb. 

-Start CoD4 MultiPlayer and join a server. (You will hear a sound when succes.) 

-When in game press the "DEL" Button on your keyboard. 

-You will see a menu on the left. 

-You can switch on/off the options by using the arrows on youre keyboard. 




Enjoy this and Keep on Seeding!
